//simple guide on crouching

1. code

// code for crouching character

get rid of void start and before code update add: 

public CharacterController PlayerHeight;             lets control height
public float normalHeight, crouchHeight;             makes public flecible numbers for normal height and crouching height

in void update add:

if(Input.GetKeydown(Keycode.c))
{
PlayerHeight.height = crouchingHeight;               when you press c change to crouch position
}
if(Input.GetKeydown(Keycode.c))
{
crouchingHeight.height = normalheight;                when you press c change to normal position
}
2. attaching script

give script to player 

in player height drag player from hierachy

in normal height set to 1

in crouching height set to 0.8





